Section.Catchline: More stringent local provisions not preempted by ss. 496.401-496.424.

SectionBody.Text: Sections 496.401-496.424 do not preempt more stringent county or municipal provisions or restrict local units of government from adopting more stringent provisions, and, in such case, such provisions must be complied with if the registrant desires to solicit within the geographic district of such local unit of government.
